"إشعارات المدين للعملاء <accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes.rst:95
msgid ""
"To record a debit note, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> "
