"اليومية الأولي. ونتيجة لذلك، يتم وضع علامة :guilabel:`غير مدفوع` على الفاتورة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:197
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the |sdd| rejection with the "
