"customer will need to have the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` set on "
"their :guilabel:`Sales and Purchase` tab of the contact record. To do so, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Order --> Customers`, "
"or :menuselection:`Contacts app --> Contacts`. Then, select a customer or "
"contact to set the fiscal position on."
msgstr ""
"Should the :guilabel:`Detect Automatically` checkbox not be ticked, each "
"customer will need to have the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` set on "
"their :guilabel:`Sales and Purchase` tab of the contact record. To do so, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Order --> Customers`, "
"or :menuselection:`Contacts app --> Contacts`. Then, select a customer or "
"contact to set the fiscal position on."

