#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:39
msgid "Automatically"
msgstr "تلقائياً "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:41
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can be automatically created by sending an email to "
"an :ref:`email alias <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` associated "
"with the purchase journal, or by :ref:`uploading a PDF <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/manual-upload>`."
msgstr ""
"يمكن إنشاء فواتير الموردين تلقائيًا عن طريق إرسال بريد إلكتروني إلى "
":ref:`عنوان بريد إلكتروني مستعار <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` "
"مرتبط بيومية الشراء، أو عن طريق :ref:`تحميل ملف PDF <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/manual-upload>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the bill is uploaded, the PDF document appears on the right side of the "
"screen, making it easy to fill in the bill information."
msgstr ""
"بمجرد تحميل الفاتورة، تظهر وثيقة PDF على الجانب الأيمن من الشاشة، مما يسهل "
"ملء معلومات الفاتورة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:48
msgid ""
"Bills can be :doc:`digitized <vendor_bills/invoice_digitization>` for "
"automatic completion and :ref:`matched with purchase orders <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>` to replace OCR-detected data with "
"the existing purchase order's details."
msgstr ""
"يمكن :doc:`رقمنة الفواتير <vendor_bills/invoice_digitization>` للإكمال "
"التلقائي و:ref:`مطابقتها مع أوامر الشراء <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"vendor-bills-matching-po>` لاستبدال البيانات المكتشفة بواسطة OCR بتفاصيل أمر "
"الشراء الموجود."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:52
msgid ""
"Services such as digitizing scanned or PDF vendor bills in Odoo "
"require :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) </applications/essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>` credits."
msgstr ""
"تتطلب خدمات مثل رقمنة فواتير الموردين الممسوحة ضوئيًا أو بصيغة PDF في Odoo "
"أرصدة :doc:`الشراء داخل التطبيق (IAP) </applications/essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:55
msgid ""
"To automatically post bills from selected vendors, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors` and select the "
"relevant vendor. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, under "
"the :guilabel:`Automation` section, update the :guilabel:`Auto-post bills` "
"field  with one of the following options:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:105
msgid ":guilabel:`Always`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`دائمًا`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Ask after 3 validations without edits`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`السؤال بعد 3 تحققات بدون تعديلات`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Never`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`أبدًا`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:65
msgid ""
":ref:`Vendor bills matching with purchase orders <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`مطابقة فواتير الموردين مع أوامر الشراء <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"vendor-bills-matching-po>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:71
msgid "Bill completion"
msgstr "إكمال الفاتورة"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:73
msgid ""
"Whether the bill is created manually or automatically, make sure the "
"following fields are appropriately completed:"
msgstr ""
"سواء تم إنشاء الفاتورة يدويًا أو تلقائيًا، تأكد من إكمال الحقول التالية بشكل "
"مناسب:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: Odoo automatically fills in some information based on "
"the information on the vendor's contact record as well as previous purchase "
"orders and bills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`المورد`: يملأ Odoo تلقائيًا بعض المعلومات بناءً على المعلومات "
"الموجودة في سجل جهة اتصال المورد بالإضافة إلى أوامر الشراء والفواتير السابقة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill Reference`: Add the sales order reference provided by the "
"vendor. This field is used to :ref:`match <accounting/payments/payments-"
"matching>` the products when they are received."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`مرجع الفاتورة`: أضف مرجع أمر البيع الذي قدمه المورد. يُستخدم هذا "
"الحقل ل:ref:`مطابقة <accounting/payments/payments-matching>` المنتجات عند "
"استلامها."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto-Complete`: Select a past bill/purchase order to complete the "
"document automatically. The :guilabel:`Vendor` field should be completed "
"before completing this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`الإكمال التلقائي`: اختر فاتورة/أمر شراء سابق لإكمال المستند "
"تلقائيًا. يجب إكمال حقل :guilabel:`المورد` قبل إكمال هذا الحقل."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Bill Date`: Select the document's issuance date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`تاريخ الفاتورة`: اختر تاريخ إصدار المستند."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounting Date`: Update the document's accounting registration "
"date if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`التاريخ المحاسبي`: قم بتحديث تاريخ التسجيل المحاسبي للمستند إذا "
"لزم الأمر."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Reference`: The :guilabel:`Memo` field automatically "
"includes the payment reference once the payment is registered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`مرجع الدفع`: يتضمن حقل :guilabel:`مذكرة` تلقائيًا مرجع الدفع بمجرد "
"تسجيل الدفع."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipient Bank`: Indicates the account number to which the "
"payment will be made. This field is required when paying via batch payment "
"files (such as :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` "
"and :doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`البنك المستلم`: يشير إلى رقم الحساب الذي سيتم الدفع إليه. هذا "
"الحقل مطلوب عند الدفع عبر ملفات الدفع الدفعية (مثل :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-"
"electronic-transfers>` و :doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date` or :guilabel:`Payment Terms` must be specified for the "
"bill payment."
msgstr ""
"يجب تحديد :guilabel:`تاريخ الاستحقاق` أو :guilabel:`شروط الدفع` لدفع الفاتورة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select which journal should record the bill and in "
"which :doc:`currency <get_started/multi_currency>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`اليومية`: حدد اليومية التي يجب أن تسجل الفاتورة وب:doc:`أي عملة "
"<get_started/multi_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:101
msgid ""
"If the bill line does not correspond to an existing product in the database, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(bars)` icon to enter a "
"description for the bill line without linking it to a product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:105
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog and view all items in an organized display, "
"click :doc:`Catalog </applications/essentials/product_catalog>`. When the "
"products and quantities are selected, click :guilabel:`Back to Bill` to "
"return to the vendor bill; the selected catalog items will appear in the "
"vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:111
msgid ""
"Multiple bills for the same purchase order may be issued if the vendor is on "
"back-order and sends invoices as products are shipped or if the vendor sends "
"partial bills or requests a deposit. In this case, multiple bills may have "
"the same :guilabel:`Bill Reference`."
msgstr ""
"قد يتم إصدار فواتير متعددة لنفس أمر الشراء إذا كان المورد في حالة نقص "
"المخزون ويرسل الفواتير عند شحن المنتجات أو إذا أرسل المورد فواتير جزئية أو "
"طلب عربونًا. في هذه الحالة، قد يكون لفواتير متعددة نفس :guilabel:`مرجع "
"الفاتورة`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:118
msgid "Bill confirmation"
msgstr "تأكيد الفاتورة"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:120
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the document is completed. The status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based on the vendor "
"bill information. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each vendor bill a unique "
"number from a defined :doc:`sequence <vendor_bills/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"انقر على :guilabel:`تأكيد` عند اكتمال المستند. يتغير الحالة إلى "
":guilabel:`مُرحَّل`، ويتم إنشاء قيد يومية بناءً على معلومات فاتورة المورد. عند "
"التأكيد، يخصص Odoo لكل فاتورة مورد رقمًا فريدًا من :doc:`تسلسل <vendor_bills/"
"sequence>` محدد."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, a vendor bill can no longer be updated. "
"Click :guilabel:`Reset to draft` if changes are required."
msgstr ""
"بمجرد تأكيدها، لا يمكن تحديث فاتورة المورد. انقر على :guilabel:`إعادة تعيين "
"إلى مسودة` إذا كانت هناك حاجة لإجراء تغييرات."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:131
msgid "Self-billing"
msgstr "الفوترة الذاتية"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:133
msgid ""
"Self-billing is a workflow where a customer generates a vendor bill on the "
"supplier's behalf and sends a copy to the supplier for their records. It "
"removes the need for the supplier to send the customer a vendor bill and is "
"common in industries where the customer has more reliable transaction data. "
"It also reduces payment time as the customer does not have to wait for the "
"supplier to issue a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"الفوترة الذاتية هي سير عمل حيث يقوم العميل بإنشاء فاتورة مورد نيابة عن "
"المورد ويرسل نسخة إلى المورد لسجلاته. يلغي الحاجة إلى أن يرسل المورد فاتورة "
"مورد إلى العميل وهو شائع في الصناعات التي يكون فيها لدى العميل بيانات معاملات "
"أكثر موثوقية. كما أنه يقلل من وقت الدفع حيث لا يتعين على العميل انتظار المورد "
"لإصدار فاتورة مورد."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:139
