#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:81
msgid ""
"The Brazilian localization package ensures compliance with Brazilian fiscal "
"and accounting regulations. It includes tools for managing taxes, fiscal "
"positions, reporting, and a predefined chart of accounts tailored to "
"Brazil’s standards."
msgstr ""
"تضمن حزمة التوطين البرازيلية الامتثال للوائح الضريبية والمحاسبية البرازيلية. "
