#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:548
msgid ""
"Reimbursement for purchasing goods or services must be given to employees in "
"a dependency relationship (full-time employee)."
msgstr ""
"يجب منح تعويض عن شراء سلع أو خدمات للموظفين في علاقة تبعية (موظف بدوام كامل)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:550
msgid ""
"Members of collegiate bodies have provided services in the exercise of their "
"function."
msgstr "قدم أعضاء الهيئات الجماعية خدمات في ممارسة وظيفتهم."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:552
msgid ""
"In these cases, a :ref:`purchase liquidation journal <localizations/ecuador/"
