#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:164
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send` window, select :guilabel:`NAV 3.0` and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"في نافذة :guilabel:`إرسال`، حدد :guilabel:`NAV 3.0` وانقر على "
":guilabel:`إرسال`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:166
msgid "When an invoice is sent to NAV 3.0, Odoo does the following:"
msgstr "عند إرسال فاتورة إلى NAV 3.0، تقوم Odoo بما يلي:"

