":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:459
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:460
msgid ""
":ref:`Company Info <general/companies/company>`: the **seller**'s full "
"credentials (VAT/TIN number, name, full address);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:462
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`: the **buyer**'s VAT/TIN number (on the partner form);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:463
msgid ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:465
msgid ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"
msgstr ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:467
msgid "It is a domestic transaction (i.e., the partner is from Italy);"
