#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:468
msgid ""
"Your company's **required fields** (:guilabel:`VAT Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, and full "
