#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:483
msgid ""
"Internal reverse charge transactions (see :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` and :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) are exported as "
"`TD16` if the following conditions are met:"
