#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:756
msgid ""
"To test the printer configuration, the physical device must first be "
"obtained and registered with the relevant authorities."
msgstr ""
"لاختبار تكوين الطابعة، يجب أولاً الحصول على الجهاز الفعلي وتسجيله لدى السلطات "
"المعنية."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:762
msgid "Setting up the printer to work with Odoo"
msgstr "إعداد الطابعة للعمل مع Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:764
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are meant to work only in the local network. This means the "
"printer and the device running :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` must be connected to the same network."
msgstr ""
"الطابعات المالية مصممة للعمل فقط في الشبكة المحلية. هذا يعني أن الطابعة "
"والجهاز الذي يشغل :doc:`نقطة البيع Odoo </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` "
"يجب أن يكونا متصلين بنفس الشبكة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:768
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are typically configured to use HTTP by default. To ensure "
"compatibility with Odoo, the settings must be updated to enable HTTPS "
"support on the printer. This can be done using either the EpsonFPWizard "
"configuration software or the keyboard connected to the printer."
msgstr ""
"عادةً ما يتم تكوين الطابعات المالية لاستخدام HTTP بشكل افتراضي. لضمان التوافق "
"مع Odoo، يجب تحديث الإعدادات لتمكين دعم HTTPS على الطابعة. يمكن القيام بذلك "
"باستخدام برنامج تكوين EpsonFPWizard أو لوحة المفاتيح المتصلة بالطابعة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:772
msgid "To set up the fiscal printer using the keyboard, follow these steps:"
msgstr "لإعداد الطابعة المالية باستخدام لوحة المفاتيح، اتبع هذه الخطوات:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:778
msgid "Type `34`. The screen displays :guilabel:`Web Server`."
msgstr "اكتب `34`. تعرض الشاشة :guilabel:`Web Server`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:779
msgid ""
"Press :guilabel:`Contante` 3 times until the screen displays :guilabel:`Web "
"Server: SSL`."
msgstr ""
"اضغط :guilabel:`Contante` 3 مرات حتى تعرض الشاشة :guilabel:`Web Server: SSL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:780
msgid "To turn the value `0` into a `1`, press :guilabel:`X`."
msgstr "لتحويل القيمة `0` إلى `1`، اضغط :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:781
msgid "To confirm, press :guilabel:`Contante` 3 times."
msgstr "للتأكيد، اضغط :guilabel:`Contante` 3 مرات."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:784
msgid ""
"Then, log in to the printer with the device that runs :doc:`Odoo Point of "
"Sale </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` so it recognizes the printer's "
"certificate."
msgstr ""
"بعد ذلك، قم بتسجيل الدخول إلى الطابعة باستخدام الجهاز الذي يشغل :doc:`نقطة "
"البيع Odoo </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` حتى يتعرف على شهادة الطابعة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:787
msgid "To approve and install the printer's certificate, follow these steps:"
msgstr "للموافقة على شهادة الطابعة وتثبيتها، اتبع هذه الخطوات:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:789
msgid ""
"Access the printer by opening a web browser and entering `https://<ip-of-"
"your-printer>` in the address bar. A :guilabel:`Warning: Potential Security "
"Risk Ahead` security message appears."
msgstr ""
"الوصول إلى الطابعة عن طريق فتح متصفح ويب وإدخال `https://<ip-of-your-printer>"
"` في شريط العنوان. تظهر رسالة أمان :guilabel:`تحذير: خطر أمني محتمل`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:791
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Advanced` to show the certificate approval options."
msgstr "انقر فوق :guilabel:`متقدم` لإظهار خيارات الموافقة على الشهادة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:792
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Proceed` to validate the certificate."
msgstr "انقر فوق :guilabel:`متابعة` للتحقق من صحة الشهادة."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:794
msgid ""
"Then, to ensure :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` is configured with the fiscal printer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Connected Devices` section, add the IP address in "
"the :guilabel:`Italian Fiscal Printer IP address` and enable :guilabel:`Use "
"HTTPS`."
msgstr ""
"بعد ذلك، للتأكد من تكوين :doc:`نقطة البيع Odoo </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` مع الطابعة المالية، انتقل إلى :menuselection:`نقطة البيع --> "
"الإعدادات --> الإعدادات`. في قسم :guilabel:`الأجهزة المتصلة`، أضف عنوان IP في "
":guilabel:`عنوان IP للطابعة المالية الإيطالية` وفعّل :guilabel:`استخدام HTTPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:802
msgid "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"
msgstr "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:804
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` is a payment method widely used in Italy "
"where vendors request payments through their bank, which forwards the "
"request to the customer's own bank and takes responsibility for the "
"collection. This enables payment automation and reduces risks for the vendor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:808
msgid ""
"The vendor generally uploads a fixed-format text file with the list of "
"payments to the bank's web portal."
msgstr ""
"يقوم البائع عمومًا بتحميل ملف نصي بتنسيق ثابت يحتوي على قائمة المدفوعات إلى "
"بوابة الويب الخاصة بالبنك."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:812
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)` are exclusively for **domestic payments** "
"in Italy. For recurring international payments, please use `SEPA Direct Debt "
"(SDD) <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:820
msgid ""
"Check that the `l10n_it_riba` module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr "تحقق من أن وحدة `l10n_it_riba` :ref:`مثبتة <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:821
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:823
msgid "Fill out the required :guilabel:`SIA Code`."
msgstr "املأ :guilabel:`رمز SIA` المطلوب."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "The company's SIA code"
msgstr "رمز SIA الخاص بالشركة"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:829
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SIA Code` identifies businesses within the Italian banking "
"network and is used to receive money through specific payment methods. It "
"consists of one letter and four digits (e.g., T1234) and can usually be "
"found on the bank's portal or obtained by contacting the bank."
msgstr ""
"يحدد :guilabel:`رمز SIA` الشركات داخل الشبكة المصرفية الإيطالية ويُستخدم لتلقي "
"الأموال من خلال طرق دفع محددة. يتكون من حرف واحد وأربعة أرقام (مثل T1234) "
"ويمكن عادةً العثور عليه على بوابة البنك أو الحصول عليه من خلال الاتصال بالبنك."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:834
msgid "Ensure the Company's bank account has an Italian IBAN."
msgstr "تأكد من أن الحساب المصرفي للشركة يحتوي على رقم IBAN إيطالي."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:837
msgid "How to configure :doc:`Bank Accounts <../accounting/bank>`"
msgstr "كيفية تكوين :doc:`الحسابات المصرفية <../accounting/bank>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:842
msgid "Accept Ri.Ba. for your invoices"
msgstr "قبول Ri.Ba. لفواتيرك"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:844
msgid ""
"Payments of type :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` can be registered from "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` (:menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Invoices`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:848
msgid ""
"Make sure that your invoice involves a Partner that has a bank account with "
"an Italian IBAN."
msgstr "تأكد من أن فاتورتك تتضمن شريكًا لديه حساب مصرفي برقم IBAN إيطالي."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:850
msgid "Then, all Payments must be grouped in a **Batch Payment**."
msgstr "بعد ذلك، يجب تجميع جميع المدفوعات في **دفعة مدفوعات**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:853
msgid ":doc:`Batch Payments <../accounting/payments>`"
msgstr ":doc:`دفعات المدفوعات <../accounting/payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:854
msgid ":doc:`Create a Batch Payment <../accounting/payments/batch>`"
msgstr ":doc:`إنشاء دفعة مدفوعات <../accounting/payments/batch>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:856
msgid ""
"Once you press the :guilabel:`Validate` button for the Batch Payment, "
"the :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` file is generated and attached to the "
"Batch Payment, so you can download it and upload it through your bank's web "
"portal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "The Ri.Ba. file attached"
msgstr "ملف Ri.Ba. المرفق"

