#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:40
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Companies`, "
"click :guilabel:`Update info`, and ensure the following company information "
"is complete and up-to-date."
