"**Veri*Factu** is the Spanish Tax Agency's verifiable invoice issuance "
"system. It is mandatory for most taxpayers in Spain, except for those who "
"use the SII system or are under a regional tax regime (i.e., TicketBai)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:198
